ildren":[],"tail":", the recommendations of the Advisory Board developed under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t7/s3123/g"},"text":"section 3123(g) of this title","children":[],"tail":", and the recommendations of the Technology Board developed under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t7/s3123a/d"},"text":"section 3123a(d) of this title","children":[],"tail":"”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1990—Par. (2). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/101/624"},"text":"Pub. L. 101–624","children":[],"tail":" amended par. (2) generally. Prior to amendment, par. (2) read as follows: “the statements of recommendations of the Joint Council developed pursuant to the provisions of "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t7/s3122/d/2/G"},"text":"section 3122(d)(2)(G) of this title","children":[],"tail":" and the statement of recommendations of the Advisory Board developed pursuant to the provisions of "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t7/s3123/f/2/E"},"text":"section 3123(f)(2)(E) of this title","children":[],"tail":"; and”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1985—Par. (4). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/99/198"},"text":"Pub. L. 99–198","children":[],"tail":" struck out par. (4) which provided for inclusion “in the report of "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1984-01-01"},"text":"January 1, 1984","children":[],"tail":", the Secretary’s needs assessment developed pursuant to the provisions of "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t7/s3121/11"},"text":"section 3121(11) of this title","children":[],"tail":"”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1981—","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/97/98"},"text":"Pub. L. 97–98","children":[],"tail":" substituted in provision preceding par. (1) “January 1” for “February 1” and added par. (4)."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"statutoryNotes","id":"idef972682-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf