"date":"2000-05-15"},"text":"May 15, 2000","children":[],"tail":", of provisions of this section relating to submittal to Congress of annual report on agricultural research, extension, and teaching activities, see "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/104/66/s3003"},"text":"section 3003 of Pub. L. 104–66","children":[],"tail":", as amended, set out as a note under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t31/s1113"},"text":"section 1113 of Title 31","children":[],"tail":", Money and Finance, and page 44 of House Document No. 103–7."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
